{"tid":1216599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求平反六一二  屌你老母盧偉聰 開槍謀殺無殺傷力市民","createTime":"2019-06-13T10:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T06:28:05.000Z","uid":171273,"like":126,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"eeda54c5a045977780cd097a243605d22d204c33","tid":1216599,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:28:24.000Z","msg":"最終要求:(可以補充/整合)<br />\n<br />\n承認定性六一二為暴動事件並不恰當 且徹回政治檢控<br />\n<br />\n要求警隊高層辭職<br />\n<br />\n承認警隊管治不當:當中包括政治洗腦破壞警隊政治中立 煽動前線警員仇恨<br />\n<br />\n承認警隊過份使用暴力且公開警隊使用武力確實標準<br />\n<br />\n承認警隊濫權且公開警權確實標準<br />\n<br />\n法院裁判濫權黑警 <br />\n<br />\n提高警員招募條件 解僱學歷低且年資不足警員 從而提高警員文化<br />\n<br />\n公開聲明警隊服務對象係市民而不是政權"},{"pid":"9de10af101e39d262cbef882226304e4b8e7f6fd","tid":1216599,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:29:12.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"59858c8324116fd515c81e8455cc5dbdfd56a1b7","tid":1216599,"uid":41477,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:29:54.000Z","msg":"一定要平反<br />\n必要時告到去國際"},{"pid":"de5e0d855a2fe9b7fccdf984d91af1a70eed172f","tid":1216599,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:31:04.000Z","msg":"警務處處長盧偉聰錯誤將暴動講成騷亂好大件事架<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1216509\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1216509</a>"},{"pid":"745d2fde5fdfc5bda54eb06c9bdce17d1e440ee3","tid":1216599,"uid":260133,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:31:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a54c4f6f00620c0d07157ffb029e1c0918814e1","tid":1216599,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:31:24.000Z","msg":"死黑警 做中共港共政治機器就要付代價"},{"pid":"79d19adcd72bec211b152de6ef7070761e434792","tid":1216599,"uid":226955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"阿sir嘅英勇英蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src